                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The neutron beam intensity was determined from the",
                " measured activities induced in gold monitor foils",
                " using the 197Au(n,gamma)198Au monitor reaction.",
                "The monitor foils were measured with the same detector",
                " and in a comparable geometry as the gallium oxide",
                " target."
              ]
